I"'*<p><img src="/assets/img/tips/macos-virtualbox-no-linux.jpg" alt="How to Install macOS on VirtualBox on Linux" /></p>

<p>To be able to install <a href="https://www.apple.com/br/mac/">macOS</a> on <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linux">Linux</a> it is important to have <a href="https://www.virtualbox.org/">VirtualBox</a> installed. Then download the macOS image in .vdi and run a script in Shell.</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Remembering that this tip is for <a href="https://www.apple.com/br/macos/high-sierra/">macOS Sierra</a>.</p>
</blockquote>

<!-- QUADRADO -->
